race.description: Girls Day Out On Sale Now Plate (C3)
race.comment: MORAVIA (9) presents third-up off rich Magic Millions features. Was quickly back on track beaten 1L at the Gold Coast last time when he led them up. Has a handy 3kg claim and he will jump and run from the inside barrier. Well-bred and should have them covered. Gollan has kept HELL TO PAY (6) in and scratched the other three. The former Sydney galloper was never in the hunt at the Gold Coast fresh, but he's placed  3/3 second-up and his best metro form is solid enough. Jones rides and he can form the quinella. VOS SAVANT (11) was an easy winner at the Gold Coast and then stepped up to a 70 here over a mile and was beaten a nose. He's capable but needs to lift to match the above pair. DON'TCHA THINK (2) resumed in the NSW country and missed by 1.3L as favourite. He has more to offer but this class will test.
